 ${python3:Depends},
Description: runtime typing introspection helpers (Avalan PPA transitive)
 typing-inspection is a small helper that fastapi (and pydantic) use
 to introspect annotated generic types at runtime. Packaged for the
 Avalan PPA because fastapi requires `>= 0.4.2` and the package is
 not in Debian.
